data.description: Well maintained, move in ready (and adorable) one story home for sale in the Lakeside neighborhood. Spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath with a floor plan that flows nicely.  Two living areas with a cozy fireplace.  Galley style kitchen with gas cooking and kitchen bar counter.  Vaulted ceilings. Tile floors throughout.  Double doors lead to a huge covered patio in the backyard which is always great - rain or shine!  Mature trees in front and back yard.  Enjoy added protection with solar screens and storm door.  Cute neighborhood and elementary school nearby.  Major highways easily accessible.  Downtown San Antonio, parks, lakes, retail, and restaurants within a short drive. Assumable FHA Loan at 2.81%.
